Week5 Day2 Weather submission

Prerequisites:
requests 
python-dotenv
streamlit

Install the required libraries with the pip commands -
pip install -r requirements.txt

Running the script:

Clone the repo with "git clone"

Generate your API keys by visiting https://openweathermap.org/api .
You just need to:
Sign up for a free account
Go to "MY API keys" in your dashboard
Copy the default API key or create a new one

and enter the key in a .env file as OPENWEATHER_API_KEY=yourkey

Run the python script streamlit.py with the command:

streamlit run streamlit.py


  and voila!

